<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1945-07-30T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1945-07-30T00:00:00-05:00" n="770" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d770">
                                <note rend="inline" type="source">740.00119 Potsdam/7–3045</note>
                                <head>No. 770<lb/><hi rend="italic">Proposal by the British
                                        Delegation</hi></head>
                                <opener>
                                    <dateline rendition="#right">[<placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Babelsberg</hi></placeName>,] <date calendar="gregorian" when="1945-07-30">July 30,
                                            1945</date>.</dateline>
                                </opener>
                                <p rend="center"><hi rend="smallcaps">Austrian Reparations</hi></p>
                                <p rend="center"><hi rend="smallcaps">British Proposal</hi></p>
                                <p>Reparations will not be exacted from Austria. Removal of plant
                                    and equipment and other goods from Austria as <gloss target="#t_War1">war</gloss> booty or otherwise will, in
                                    future, be a matter to be settled by the Control Council.</p>
                            </div>
                            </body></text></TEI>